column16: Jimmy Rollins called out on strikes.
Brian Schneider hit by pitch.    Carlos Delgado to 2nd.
Damion Easley out on a sacrifice fly to left fielder Skip Schumaker.    Ryan Church scores.
Carlos Delgado singles on a ground ball to center fielder Rick Ankiel.    David Wright scores.    Ryan Church to 3rd.
Ryan Church singles on a soft line drive to left fielder Skip Schumaker.    David Wright to 2nd.
Jose Reyes flies out to right fielder Skip Schumaker.
Damion Easley singles on a soft line drive to right fielder Skip Schumaker.    Endy Chavez to 2nd.
Endy Chavez singles on a fly ball to left fielder Chris Duncan.
Fernando Tatis grounds out, shortstop Brendan Ryan to first baseman Albert Pujols.
